-- Kabel Deutschland intends to recommend Vodafone offer
-- 
-- Mon Jun 24, 2013 2:56am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/06/24/us-vodafone-kabeldeutschland-recommend-idUSBRE95N06T20130624

 

 FRANKFURT  (Reuters) - Kabel Deutschland's management said on Monday said it intended to recommend the Vodafone takeover offer to its shareholders. 
 "The Management Board of Kabel Deutschland Holding AG considers the price proposed by Vodafone attractive for shareholders and intends to recommend the offer," the company said in a statement. "In the Management Board's opinion the offer adequately reflects both the strategic value of Kabel Deutschland to Vodafone and the company's growth prospects," it added. (Reporting by Harro ten Wolde; editing by  Edward Taylor )